---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="can’t fall asleep? here’s how to fix it"
  description="struggling to fall asleep? learn what’s actually causing it and how to fix it naturally."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">guide</p>
      <h1>can’t fall asleep? here’s what’s causing it</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        if your body feels tired but your mind won’t shut off, your system is likely overstimulated and out of rhythm.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        fix the inputs, and falling asleep becomes easier again.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>common causes</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>too much screen time at night</p>
          <p>late caffeine or food</p>
          <p>overthinking or stress</p>
          <p>inconsistent sleep schedule</p>
          <p>low daytime light exposure</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what’s happening</h2>
        <p>
          your body needs a clear signal that it’s time to wind down. when light, stimulation, and timing are off,
          your brain stays alert even when you’re physically tired.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>quick reset</h2>

      <div class="content-block">
        <p>dim lights after sunset</p>
        <p>stop screens 60–90 minutes before bed</p>
        <p>keep a consistent sleep schedule</p>
        <p>get sunlight early the next morning</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">sleep</span>
        </div>
        <h2>reduce stimulation at night</h2>
        <p>
          blue light blocking glasses can help reduce stimulation and support your natural sleep rhythm.
        </p>
        <a href="/recommendations/blue-light-glasses" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">sleep</span>
        </div>
        <h2>calm the body before sleep</h2>
        <p>
          magnesium can help reduce tension and support relaxation, especially if your body feels wired at night.
        </p>
        <a href="/recommendations/magnesium" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
